These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, tea, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, lilac, black, fuchsia
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, tennis, soccer, golf
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person who likes lilac##1
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 6. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person drinking soy-milk##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
13. the person who's sport is golf is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | fanta | tea    | soy-milk   |
| Color   | mauve | black | lilac | fuchsia |
| Pet           | dog       | horse   | rabbit  | cat     |
| Sport     | baseball      | soccer   | golf    | tennis    |

