The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, writing, photography, drawing
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is the australian##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
 7. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the australian##7
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
10. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
11. the chinese is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
