There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, 7up, lemonade
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, brown, mauve, ivory
 1. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the person who likes ivory is somewhere between the fan of funk and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the fan of r&b is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the fan of folk is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the fan of hip-hop##6
 9. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Music-Genre           | hip-hop | funk | r&b | folk |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | zombie    | crime    | martial-arts    |
