 3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
 4. the french is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 5. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 7. the person eating lettuce is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person playing monopoly##7
 8. the person eating apple is not the person playing poker##6
 9. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
10. the pilot is on the left of the french##1
11. the freelancer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
12. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food         | orange      | lettuce   | apple   | pear       |
| Job   | doctor | pilot    | entrepreneur | freelancer       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| Game         | poker   | backgammon    | monopoly   | whist |

