.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
City: marseilles, venice, colone, san-francisco
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, lemon, pear
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, pink, fuchsia, amber
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, havana, alhambra, old-henry
 1. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 3. the person who likes amber is between the old-henry-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the havana-smoker##6
 6. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person eating pear##7
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
 9. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the alhambra-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| City   | venice   | san-francisco     | colone   | marseilles |
| Food       | pear   | apricot | artichoke | lemon    |
| Color      | fuchsia | amber | apricot   | pink  |
| Cigar        | old-henry | cain     | alhambra   | havana |

