.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, blue, light-blue, purple
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, daisy, zinnia
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, police-officer, writer
