 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
 4. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the chaman-smoker is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
 8. the montecristo-smoker is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
