.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, satire, mystery, comedy
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, red, yellow, chestnut
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, september, december, october
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 2. the person who likes yellow is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching satire movies##2
 5. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the person watching horror movies##7
 7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | mystery     | satire   | horror    |
| Color     | chestnut | yellow   | red | brown |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Birthday   | september       | october | june   | december    |

 